                    "uri": "at://did:plc:tbqqvyv6pjjww44glrmycaxl/app.bsky.feed.post/3mpclwr75w22e"
                  }
                },
                "text": "Yes! In a paper I recently edited, I wrote this to the author.\n\n\"You will see that reviewer 3 is an inordinate fan of Dr. ____. While I have no doubts that this work is excellent, I was unable to find the connection to your present paper and encourage you to be judicious in following their advice.\""
              },
              "bookmarkCount": 1,
              "replyCount": 1,
              "repostCount": 3,
              "likeCount": 52,
