                ],
                "reply": {
                  "parent": {
                    "cid": "bafyreibqc5qyjdjpasu7cmq6qsmwnwkfucibzdlzlvaixc6l57tjva4zxm",
                    "uri": "at://did:plc:oclqhr3bchhxe42nd3dses7g/app.bsky.feed.post/3mpcmaogios2n"
                  },
                  "root": {
                    "cid": "bafyreibrbngg63c56frz5l7bz5byu2wcnes5zv4iyr7fqpkfacnx6oegjm",
                    "uri": "at://did:plc:tbqqvyv6pjjww44glrmycaxl/app.bsky.feed.post/3mpclwr75w22e"
                  }
                },
                "text": "Editors? Do they really exist? I doubt they do.\nIt occurred to me as a referee to reject a paper which was nonsensical, and my co-reviewer did the same.\nThe journal required a \"moderate revision\" and asked me to review it again.\nIf you're ready to pay APCs, you'll get published no matter what."
              },
              "bookmarkCount": 0,
              "replyCount": 1,
              "repostCount": 0,
              "likeCount": 2,
              "quoteCount": 0,
              "indexedAt": "2026-06-28T07:01:14.567Z"
            },
            "threadContext": {}
          },
          {
