                    "uri": "at://did:plc:tbqqvyv6pjjww44glrmycaxl/app.bsky.feed.post/3mpclwr75w22e"
                  }
                },
                "text": "I'm always amazed how hands off editors can be with reviewers. \n\nI had a reviewer complain about violin plots in my paper - and he compared them to female genitalia... And I'm like, wtf editor? You allow that?"
              },
